Dragonheart Annual Holidays
                
January    19  Crimsonesti Winter Solstice  (Ash's half b-day)
Febuary    14  Day of Retribution           (Annual No-Save Day)        
June       19  Crimsonesti Summer Solstice  (Ash's b-day)
July        4  Builder Appreciation Day     (DH compliles first time'95)
August      1  Holy Purge                   (ALL DH Email is PURGED)
October    31  Celibration of Creation      (DH first opened 1995)
December   25  Day of Reconciliation        (A chance to ponder)    

